<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='274612' id='t-274612'>when they're laying the eggs.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='276077' id='t-276077'>They cannot prevent this.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='277512' id='t-277512'>They can also not medicate themselves.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='279443' id='t-279443'>But what these experiments tell us</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='281680' id='t-281680'>is that these monarchs, these mothers,
