<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='314148' id='t-314148'>and in indigenous cultures,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='315760' id='t-315760'>traditional healers often look
at animals to find new drugs.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='318595' id='t-318595'>In this way, elephants have told us
how to treat stomach upset,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='322002' id='t-322002'>and porcupines have told people
